": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"defence\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"ahockey stickon\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring finger\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"his right hand\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident, where the top of his finger was almost entirely severed, happened just two weeks before he was supposed to represent his national team in their opening match.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The incident\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"his finger\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"his national team\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"their opening match\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawson, who had originally thought his dream of athird Olympicswas over after seeing the extent of the injury, urgently consulted a plastic surgeon, who told him that it could be repaired with a wire, but the recovery process could take up to six months.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999998194653, \"rank\": 1.788328471183669e-10, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his dream\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"athird\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"a plastic surgeon\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"a wire\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"the recovery process\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"up to six months\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The surgeon said that the alternative was to amputate the affected part of the finger, and he could return to playing within 10 days.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The surgeon\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"the alternative\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"the affected part\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the finger\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"10 days\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old then opted to get the affected part removed, from the second knuckle up.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the affected part\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"the second knuckle\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawson, who won asilver medalat Tokyo 2020, told the media that the break was so bad that he passed out when he saw the extent of his injury in the changing room, but that he made an informed decision on the same day that he saw the surgeon.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999998194653, \"rank\": 1.788328471183669e-10, \"text\": \"Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dawson_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8599827997670468, \"rank\": 0.14589443008586478, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the break\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngr